        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[This week in PSC (227) | 2026-06-01]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[This week we were back to full strength. We have now dealt with all of the belated issues and all of the blockers. Paul will be shipping 5.43.11 very shortly. With the amount of changes we have had to merge, we will not be able to rush the .11 cycle, but we intend to start the work on the 5.44 RC early, to ensure that we can release with as little additional delay as possible.]]></description>
            <pubDate>2026.06.01</pubDate>
